1. Requiremment Clarification

    i. Functional Requirement

        -> Should retrive content from origin servers
        -> Must process requests from end-users
        -> Efficiently deliver cached content to end-users
        -> Efficiently search and locate cached content
        -> Should invalidate outdated cached content & remove it

    ii. Non-Functional Requirements

        -> Low Latency
        -> High Availability
        -> Global Systems



